{
  "id": "63c567d56b8d82001de41f07",
  "title": "周波数3/2倍は7半音と2cents",
  "created": 1673881558,
  "updated": 1673881712,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63c567d56b8d82001de41f07",
      "text": "周波数3/2倍は7半音と2cents",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab5e",
      "text": "from [音律の比較]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881563
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567db774b17000023ab79",
      "text": "「周波数を3/2倍したら何半音kか？」",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881564,
      "updated": 1673881599
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567fe774b17000023ab7c",
      "text": "[$ 2^{(k/12)}=3/2]をとけばよい",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881599,
      "updated": 1673881606
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567e9774b17000023ab7b",
      "text": " [$ 2^{(k/12)}=3/2]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881577,
      "updated": 1673881643
    },
    {
      "id": "63c5681e774b17000023ab7d",
      "text": " [$ \\log_2 2^{(k/12)}=\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881630,
      "updated": 1673881643
    },
    {
      "id": "63c5681e774b17000023ab7e",
      "text": " [$ k/12=\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881630,
      "updated": 1673881643
    },
    {
      "id": "63c5681e774b17000023ab7f",
      "text": " [$ k=12\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881630,
      "updated": 1673881643
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56831774b17000023ab83",
      "text": " [$ k=7.01955...]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881650,
      "updated": 1673881676
    },
    {
      "id": "63c5681e774b17000023ab80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881630,
      "updated": 1673881630
    },
    {
      "id": "63c5681f774b17000023ab81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881631,
      "updated": 1673881631
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567dc774b17000023ab7a",
      "text": "誤解",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881564,
      "updated": 1673881575
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab61",
      "text": "3/2は7半音？[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab62",
      "text": " 12半音ベースで考えると11×3/2=7.3半音",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab63",
      "text": " 3/2は周波数の話で、[音階]はその対数なので混ぜるな危険[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab64",
      "text": " 　1オクターブが周波数2倍",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab65",
      "text": " 　周波数3/2倍は:",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab66",
      "text": " 　\t`log(3/2, 2) * 12` = 7.01955...",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c56838aff09e00000f648d",
      "text": " 　\t\t追記: [$ \\log_2 (3/2)]の意味。底がオプション引数なので2番目に来てる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1673881656,
      "updated": 1673881712
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab67",
      "text": " 　　7半音と2セント",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab68",
      "text": " 「周波数を3/2倍したら何半音kか？」は[$ 2^{(k/12)}=3/2]か〜！[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab69",
      "text": "  k=[$ 12/(\\log_{3/2} 2) ]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6a",
      "text": "   =[$ 12\\log(3/2)/\\log(2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6b",
      "text": "   =7.01955...",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6c",
      "text": "  対数の底が3/2なのはおかしい[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6d",
      "text": "   底の条件は満たしているように思うのですが[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6e",
      "text": "    https://manabitimes.jp/math/1336",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab6f",
      "text": "    log2をとって[$ k=12\\log_2(3/2)]の方が素直",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab70",
      "text": "   底の条件の話ではなく「素直さ」の話でした[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab71",
      "text": "    左辺が2の指数である時にその指数を払うなら2で対数を取るのが素直",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab72",
      "text": "    [$ 2^{(k/12)}=3/2]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab73",
      "text": "    [$ \\log_2 2^{(k/12)}=\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab74",
      "text": "    [$ k/12=\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab75",
      "text": "    [$ k=12\\log_2(3/2)]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab76",
      "text": "    これが自然な変形",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab77",
      "text": "     ですね[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1673881558,
      "updated": 1673881558
    },
    {
      "id": "63c567d6774b17000023ab78",
